'''所罗门河'''（{{lang-en|Solomon River}}），也被称为'''所罗门汊'''（{{lang-en|Solomon Fork}}），是[[北美大平原|北美大平原]]中部的一条长约{{Convert|184|mi|km}}的[[河流|河流]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://viewer.nationalmap.gov/advanced-viewer/ |title = National Hydrography Dataset high-resolution flowline data |author = The National Map |publisher = U.S. Geological Survey |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-19 |archive-date = 2012-04-05 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/66gupqQDM?url=http://viewer.nationalmap.gov/viewer/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。河流位于[[美国州份|美国]]的[[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]]，是[[斯莫基希尔河|斯莫基希尔河]]的[[支流|支流]]。

== 流向及流域 ==
所羅門河由{{tsl|en|North Fork Solomon River|所羅門河北汊}}及{{tsl|en|South Fork Solomon River|所羅門河南汊}}合流而成{{sfn|U.S. Bureau of Reclamation|1984|pp=5-8}}。這兩條分汊均發源於堪薩斯州西北部的{{tsl|en|High Plains (United States)|高地平原}}，並在[[米切爾縣_(堪薩斯州)|米切爾縣]]西北部的{{tsl|en|Waconda Lake|沃孔達湖}}匯合{{sfn|U.S. Bureau of Reclamation|1984|pp=5-8}}<ref>{{Cite web |url = {{gnis3|472301}} |title = North Fork Solomon River |author = Geographic Names Information System (GNIS) |date = 1978-10-13 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-19}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = {{gnis3|485293}} |title = South Fork Solomon River |author = Geographic Names Information System (GNIS) |date = 1978-10-13 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-19}}</ref>。離開沃孔達湖後，河水會往東南方流動，先後流經{{tsl|en|Beloit, Kansas|貝洛伊特}}、[[明尼阿波利斯|明尼阿波利斯]]及{{tsl|en|Smoky Hills|煙山}}地區，並在途中與多條溪流合流<ref name="gnis"/>。所羅門河最終在[[迪金森縣_(堪薩斯州)|迪金森縣]]所羅門的南部與[[斯莫基希爾河|斯莫基希爾河]]匯合{{sfn|U.S. Bureau of Reclamation|1984|pp=5-8}}<ref name="gnis"/>。

所羅門河的流域面積為{{convert|6835|mi2|km2}}，同時它亦屬於[[密西西比河|密西西比河]]流域的一部分<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.kwo.org/Kansas%20Water%20Plan/SWP/KWP_2008/Vol_III_Docs/SOL/Rpt_SOL_Basin_Description_KWP2009.pdf |title = Solomon River Basin |author = Kansas Water Office |date = 2009 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-19 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110603230626/http://www.kwo.org/Kansas%20Water%20Plan/SWP/KWP_2008/Vol_III_Docs/SOL/Rpt_SOL_Basin_Description_KWP2009.pdf |archivedate = 2011-06-03}}</ref>。

== 命名 ==
河流被當時沿河居住的美洲原住民稱為維斯卡帕拉河（Wiskapalla River），意為「鹹水」（Salt water）<ref name="gnis"/>。另有部份原住民稱河流為「Nepaholla」，意為「山上的水」，指的是位於河谷中的{{tsl|en|Waconda Spring|沃孔達溫泉}}<ref name="Solomon Valley"/>。1744年，法國探險家以著名的[[法屬路易斯安那|法屬路易斯安那]]官員埃德梅·加蒂安·德薩蒙（Edme Gatien de Salmon）來把河流命名為薩蒙河（Salmon River），但後來因錯誤的口耳相傳而變為現時的稱謂{{sfn|Hall|1995|p=8}}。另外，河流亦有「Mahkineohe」、蘇西斯河（{{lang|fr|Rivière de Soucis}}）、所羅門溪及所羅門汊等稱呼<ref name="Solomon Valley"/>。

== 歷史 ==
早在美國殖民之前，所羅門河山谷是[[大平原印第安人|大平原印第安人]]的熱門狩獵地點，而[[波尼族|波尼族]]、[[夏延族|夏延族]]及{{tsl|en|Kaw people|堪薩人}}則沿河設立營地<ref name="Solomon Valley">{{Cite web |url = http://www.hwy24.org/about-the-valley.html |title = About the Solomon Valley |last = Von |first = Rothenberger |date = 2002 |publisher = Solomon Valley/Highway 24 Heritage Alliance |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070516004225/http://skyways.lib.ks.us/orgs/svha/about_valley.htm |archivedate = 2007-05-16}}</ref>。1712年，法國探險家{{tsl|en|Étienne de Veniard, Sieur de Bourgmont|艾蒂安·文雅德·布爾格蒙特}}探索了該地區，並聲稱該地屬於法國<ref name="Schoewe@1951">{{Cite journal |last = Schoewe |first = Walter H. |title= The Geography of Kansas: Part III. Hydrogeography |journal= Transactions of the Kansas Academy of Science |year= 1951 |volume= 54 |issue= 3 |pages= 263-329}}</ref>。1744年，一群法國探險家回到所羅門河山谷進行勘測，並為河流命名<ref name="Schoewe@1951"/><ref name="Solomon Valley"/>。1803年，[[路易斯安那購地|美國向法國購買法屬路易斯安那]]，自此所羅門河山谷便成為了美國領土的一部分。1806年，美國探險家{{tsl|en|Zebulon Pike|紀伯倫·派克}}帶領探險隊穿越所羅門河山谷，並在所羅門河北汊紮營<ref>{{Cite journal |last= Scheffer |first= Theodore H. |url= https://www.kshs.org/p/following-pike-s-expedition-from-the-smoky-hill-to-the-solomon/13066 |title= Following Pike's Expedition From the Smoky Hill to the Solomon |journal= The Kansas Historical Quarterly |year= 1947 |volume= 14 |issue= 3 |pages= 240-247 |access-date= 2020-09-19 |archive-date= 2019-12-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191216135801/https://www.kshs.org/p/following-pike-s-expedition-from-the-smoky-hill-to-the-solomon/13066 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。1850年代，美國拓荒者開始移居至所羅門河山谷，並開始逐步建立城鎮<ref name="Schoewe@1951"/>。1861年，該區域成為堪薩斯州的一部分<ref name="Solomon Valley"/>。

1944年，作為密蘇里河流域綜合發展計劃的一部分，格倫埃爾德水壩的興建方案在呈交至[[美國國會|美國國會]]的參議院191號文件內被提及，用以滿足[[斯莫基希爾河|斯莫基希爾河]]流域的防洪和灌溉需求<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.usbr.gov/projects/index.php?id=461 |title = Glen Elder Unit |author = U.S. Bureau of Reclamation |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200823194939/https://www.usbr.gov/projects/index.php?id=461 |archivedate = 2020-08-23 }}</ref>。1951年7月中旬，連場大雨導致[[堪薩斯河|堪薩斯河]]、[[密蘇里河|密蘇里河]]及其他周邊地區的水位大幅上升，最終洪水摧毀了堪薩斯州東部<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.foxnews.com/us/1951-flood-painting-sells-for-nearly-1-9m-in-nyc |title = 1951 flood painting sells for nearly $1.9M in NYC |author = Associated Press |date = 2011-05-19 |publisher = Fox News |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190711205655/https://www.foxnews.com/us/1951-flood-painting-sells-for-nearly-1-9m-in-nyc |archivedate = 2019-07-11}}</ref>。為了防止災難重演，{{tsl|en|United States Bureau of Reclamation|美國墾務局}}及[[美國陸軍工兵部隊|美國陸軍工兵部隊]]提出多項防洪方案，其中包括在所羅門河流經的{{tsl|en|Glen Elder, Kansas|格倫埃爾德 (堪薩斯州)|格倫埃爾德}}附近興建水壩<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://pubs.usgs.gov/fs/2001/0041/report.pdf |title = The 1951 Floods in  Kansas Revisited |author = U.S. Geological Survey |date = 2001 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170301163631/https://pubs.usgs.gov/fs/2001/0041/report.pdf |archivedate = 2017-03-01 }}</ref>。1969年，美國墾務局及美國陸軍工兵部隊完成格倫埃爾德水壩（Glen Elder Dam）及其水庫{{tsl|en|Waconda Lake|沃孔達湖}}的建設<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.usbr.gov/projects/pdf.php?id=161 |title = Glen Elder Unit, Solomon Division, Pick-Sloan Missouri Basin Program |last = Rucker |first = Kevin E. |date = 2001 |publisher = Bureau of Reclamation |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190928212830/https://www.usbr.gov/projects/pdf.php?id=161 |archivedate = 2019-09-28 }}</ref>。

== 生態 ==
一份2002年的研究確定所羅門河的流量會影響魚類的數量，指流量較低的河段（如位於柯溫水庫及韋伯斯特水庫上游的河段）其魚類數目較少<ref name="Eberle, Hargett, Wenke & Mandrak@2002">{{Cite journal |last1 = Eberle |first1 = Mark E. |last2 = Hargett |first2 = Eric G. |last3 = Wenke |first3 = Thomas L. |last4 = Mandrak |first4 = Nicholas E. |title= Changes in Fish Assemblages, Solomon River Basin, Kansas: Habitat Alterations, Extirpations, and Introductions |journal= Transactions of the Kansas Academy of Science |year= 2002 |volume= 105 |issue= 3 |pages= 178-192}}</ref>。同時，研究指出現時所羅門河流域內約有32%的本地物種消失，而在目前的魚類種群中約51%是由外來物種組成<ref name="Eberle, Hargett, Wenke & Mandrak@2002"/>。另外，有科研人員亦在流域內收集了河水、沉積物、大型無脊椎動物和魚類樣本，並進行[[硒|硒]]濃度分析，發現所有樣本的硒含量均超過懷疑會造成魚類繁殖障礙的水平<ref>{{Cite journal |last1 = May |first1 = Thomas W. |last2 = Fairchild |first2 = James F. |last3 = Petty |first3 = Jim D. |last4 = Walther |first4 = Michael J. |last5 = Lucero |first5 = Jeff |last6 = Delvaux |first6 = Mike |last7 = Manring |first7 = Jill |last8 = Armbruster |first8 = Mike |title= An evaluation of selenium concentrations in water, sediment, invertebrates, and fish from the Solomon River Basin |url = https://archive.org/details/sim_environmental-monitoring-and-assessment_2008-02_137_1-3/page/213 |journal= Environmental Monitoring and Assessment |year= 2008 |volume= 137 |pages= 213-232}}</ref>。

